item.description: Our lives, our past, is a thread from the tapestry that we are woven from, the roots we have grown from. Many times we may discover parts of our past we may be ashamed of, afraid of, or perhaps even angered by; but ultimately all of it is what made us who we are. It is to us then, to look upon our past with the unflinching eye and draw from it inspiration and strength, regardless of the trials and tribulations found there.
